<paragraph id="DC04070F9A004346FF57CE93FF32339F" blockId="4.[178,1085,902,983]" pageId="4" pageNumber="1239">
C o m m e n t: 
<taxonomicName id="1BBB7C8C9A004346FE86CE93FDEE33D3" authorityName="COIFFAIT" authorityYear="1983" box="[355,552,902,923]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Othius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="1239" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pokharensis">
<emphasis id="EECFDB1D9A004346FE86CE93FDEE33D3" box="[355,552,902,923]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="1239">Othius pokharensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is the most widespread 
<taxonomicName id="1BBB7C8C9A004346FCC5CE93FC7233D4" box="[800,948,902,924]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Othius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="1239" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="undetermined">
<emphasis id="EECFDB1D9A004346FCC5CE93FCA533D3" box="[800,867,902,923]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="1239">Othius</emphasis>
species
</taxonomicName>
in the Himalaya, its distribution ranging from 
<collectingRegion id="1E7FC9ED9A004346FDC5CEB1FD1A33F2" box="[544,732,932,954]" country="India" name="Himachal Pradesh" pageId="4" pageNumber="1239">Himachal Pradesh</collectingRegion>
to 
<collectingRegion id="1E7FC9ED9A004346FCE1CEB1FC8B33F2" box="[772,845,932,954]" country="India" name="Sikkim" pageId="4" pageNumber="1239">Sikkim</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation id="B82A7AFE9A004346FCBBCEB1FC2D33F1" author="ASSING V" box="[862,1003,932,953]" pageId="4" pageNumber="1239" pagination="293 - 342" refId="ref6933" refString="ASSING V. (1998): A revision of Othius STEPHENS. V. The species of the Himalayan region (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae, Xantholininae). - Beitrage zur Entomologie, Berlin 48 (1): 293 - 342." type="journal article" year="1998">ASSING 1998</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="B82A7AFE9A004346FC1CCEB1FBFF33F1" author="ASSING V" box="[1017,1081,932,953]" pageId="4" pageNumber="1239" pagination="727 - 752" refId="ref7072" refString="ASSING V. (2003 a): A revision of Othius STEPHENS. IX. New taxa, new synonyms, additional records, and a checklist of species (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae, Staphylininae, Othiini), pp. 727 - 752. - In: CUCCODORO G. &amp; R. A. B. LESCHEN (eds), Systematics of Coleoptera: Papers celebrating the retirement of Ivan Lobl. Memoirs on Entomology International Vol. 17, Associated Publishers, Gainesville, Florida." type="journal article" year="2003">2003a</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="B82A7AFE9A004346FF57CED4FF2F339F" author="ASSING V" box="[178,233,961,983]" pageId="4" pageNumber="1239" pagination="51 - 67" refId="ref7213" refString="ASSING V. (2005): A revision of Othiini. XIV. New species, new synonyms, and new records (Insecta: Coleoptera: Staphylinidae). - Entomological Problems 35 (1): 51 - 67." type="journal article" year="2005">2005</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
